{{Infobox comics creator | name = Przemysław Truściński | image = Truscinski_Przemyslaw.jpg | imagesize = 150 | caption = Przemysław Truściński at 21st International Festival of Comics and Games in Łódź | birth_name = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1970|12|15|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Siedlce]] | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = [[Poles|Polish]] | area = Artist | alias = Trust | signature = | notable works = | awards = | website = http://www.trusthead.com }} '''Przemysław Truściński''' (born 15 December 1970 in [[Siedlce]]) [[Poles|Polish]] [[comics artist]]. He graduated [[Academy of Fine Arts In Łódź]]. He uses the ''Trust'' nickname.<ref name="Gildia">{{cite web | url = http://www.komiks.gildia.pl/tworcy/przemyslaw_truscinski/ | title = Przemysław Truściński (Trust) | language = pl | accessdate = December 19, 2013 | publisher = Gildia.pl sp. z.o.o. | issn = 2300-004X | work = Gildia.pl}}</ref>
==Biography== He has worked as a comics artist for [[Gazeta Wyborcza]], [[Playboy]], [[Machina (magazine)|Machina]] and [[Newsweek]] and as an advertisement artist in [[Pepsi]] and [[Nescafe]]. Awarded several prizes in [[International Festival of Comics and Games]] in Łódź. His short stories anthology ''Trust - historia choroby'' was published 2003, but numerous other short comics were published in various magazines and anthologies.<ref name="Gildia"/> His work on press comic was gathered in the ''Komiks W-wa'' compilation.<ref name="Gildia2">{{cite web | url = http://www.komiks.gildia.pl/komiksy/komiks-w-wa/1 | title = Komiks W-wa | language = pl | accessdate = December 19, 2013 | publisher = Gildia.pl sp. z.o.o. | issn = 2300-004X | work = Gildia.pl}}</ref>
He is well known for his [[The Witcher]] game project.<ref name="Culture">{{cite web | url = http://culture.pl/pl/tworca/przemyslaw-trust-truscinski | title = Przemysław Trust Truściński | work = Culture.pl | author = Łukasz Chmielewski | date = August 2013 | language = pl | publisher = [[Adam Mickiewicz Institute]] | accessdate = December 19, 2013}}</ref>
==Awards== * 2013: [[Cross of Merit (Poland)|Silver Cross of Merit]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.prezydent.pl/aktualnosci/ordery-i-odznaczenia/art,1235,odznaczenia-w-69-rocznice-powstania-warszawskiego.html | title = Odznaczenia w 69. rocznicę Powstania Warszawskiego | accessdate = December 19, 2013 | publisher = Kancelaria Prezydenta RP | work = Prezydent.pl | date = July 31, 2013 | language = pl}}</ref>
